            "desc": "Record a ZK-verified consent on-chain.\nIMPORTANT: `proof` and `public_inputs` MUST be the first two parameters so the AlgoPlonk-generated logicsig finds them at app_args[1] and app_args[2]. The logicsig verifies the PLONK proof before approving this transaction. If we reach this line, the proof was cryptographically valid \u2014 no trusted oracle.\nDuplicate submissions are rejected via the box key.",
